{"tid":519632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一年前涉偷拍少女裙底　休班警被控破壞公眾體統罪】","createTime":"2018-01-04T14:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T15:36:06.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ac90a136752150259cad082469da08ec908afef","tid":519632,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:26:15.000Z","msg":"因連環爆出醜聞而聲譽受損的香港警隊，又有警員涉偷拍裙底被捕。<br />\n<br />\n一名33歲姓刑的休班警員，去年1月21日涉嫌在旺角港鐵站的扶手電梯，用手提電話偷拍一名16歲少女裙底。警方經進一步調查及徵詢法律意見後，昨日（1月3日）拘捕該名涉案警員。<br />\n<br />\n該名休班警被控以一項破壞公眾體統罪，案件將於下周四（1月11日）在西九龍裁判法院提堂"},{"pid":"f88cda99a9147f56661821905d7337b4fa9c6956","tid":519632,"uid":34869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"對自己人就搵條輕到唔輕既罪出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff14f0b4eab4ab2315e4da6cf76240fb383f424","tid":519632,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f88cda99a9147f56661821905d7337b4fa9c6956","tid":519632,"uid":34869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"對自己人就搵條輕到唔輕既罪出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:30:26.000Z","msg":"嚴重打擊休班警既士氣"},{"pid":"7da62c44d24f77b5bb572c08f0c76db70cc07834","tid":519632,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:34:22.000Z","msg":"服務市民"},{"pid":"67b28504fb1e6a2d2f1dc7004264096a4694c9e2","tid":519632,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大驚小怪！！！&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt; <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿犬攪野，唔洗你教！！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/223314_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fuploa